name: The 7 Talisman of Work: Hammer
description:
This Golden item is a manifestation of pure magnificence.
None is so sure of where and when it was found or the date of its creation but the heart of this tool is one of fire and creative work.
It can carve, shape and chip away at diamond shaped mounds of sugar so it is not a weapon but a guardian of the sweet.
Feel it glisten in your presence.
Hold it and may You never be put out of a trade or work.
